item.title: CVE-2018-10632|2024-08-05T07:46:46.303Z -- moxa -- nport%205210%2C%205230%2C%20and%205232
item.description: In Moxa NPort 5210, 5230, and 5232 versions 2.9 build 17030709 and prior, the amount of resources requested by a malicious actor are not restricted, allowing for a denial-of-service condition.
